===DIFFERENCES===
everyday-categories
-----------------
words that are adjectives and not nouns return things from 'bighugethesaurus' I can't use...
affectionate +becomes+ affection
afraid +becomes+ anxiety 
amused +becomes+ amusement
angry +becomes + anger
bored +becomes + boredom
confident +becomes+ confidence
content +becomes+ satisfaction
disappointed +becomes+ disappointment
excited +becomes+ excitement
happy +becomes+ joy
interested +becomes+ curiosity
loving +becomes+ love
pleased +becomes+ pride
relaxed +becomes+ calmness
sad + becomes+ sadness
satisfied +becomes+ harmony
worried +becomes+ worry

**********************************
========
for occ-categories
--------
I mostly keep the same as below ( I am noticing an overlap ;-) )

    <item name="admiration"/>
    <item name="anger"/>
    <item name="disappointment"/>
    <item name="distress"/>
    <item name="fear"/>
    <item name="fears-confirmed"/>    
    <item name="gloating"/>
    <item name="gratification"/>
    <item name="gratitude"/>
    <item name="happy-for"/>
    <item name="hate"/> 
    <item name="hope"/>
    <item name="joy"/>
    <item name="love"/>
    <item name="pity"/> 
    <item name="pride"/>
    <item name="relief"/> 
    <item name="remorse"/> 
    <item name="reproach"/>
    <item name="resentment"/>
    <item name="satisfaction"/>
    <item name="shame"/>

========but here are the exceptions:========
fears-confirmed +becomes+ dread
gloating +becomes+ triumph
happy-for +becomes+ appreciation
shame +becomes+ embarrassment

